---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Lenny Chen">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-heading)]">About</h1>
  <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      My name is Lenny, and I'm a <strong class="text-[var(--color-heading)]">technical writer</strong> who mainly works in developer docs (one day when I'm rich I will do board game manuals pro-bono perhaps).
      I am passionate about learning new technologies, quick to help others, and love the feeling of being proud of something I made.
    </p>
    <p>
      In my spare time, I'm an impulsive reader (working on being more consistent), hobbyist translator, amateur volleyball player,
      under-motivated gaymer, and disaster-prone chef.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm also a big fan of the cinema. Since 2024, I've been reviewing every single film I watch on <a href="https://letterboxd.com/lennessy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:text-[var(--color-link-hover)] underline transition-colors">Letterboxd</a>. I think I have great taste. If you are a big cinephile yourself, you should give me a follow and let's talk about movies. If you only go occasionally, feel free to check <a href="/reviews" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:text-[var(--color-link-hover)] underline transition-colors">here</a> to see how I liked a movie before you decide whether you should see it. If you are not a movie person, well you should be. It's <i>the</i> art form of our time. 
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
